Class Rebind

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cisco.dvbu.ps.deploytool.gui.core.module.rebind.Rebind

extends java.lang.Object

    Bean object for rebind module rebind records. Intended to be serialized/deserialized by Jackson into/from JSON.
